{"tid":2050813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[建議]今晚大家右手拎蠟燭/手機嘅時候 左手可唔可以做呢個手勢?","createTime":"2020-06-04T10:53:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T13:57:59.000Z","uid":225100,"like":5,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5b6ddf9dd0e34e72afb6b6cefbfc74b69c126020","tid":2050813,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T10:53:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1BOJs48.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1BOJs48.gif&h=99ff3ad5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n出自<em>The Hunger Games</em><br />\n意思係向對象表達<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>感謝、愛和尊敬</strong></span><br />\n個人覺得係一個對31年前抗爭的六四死難者們來說係非常合適嘅手勢<br />\n戲入面都係因為有人死女主角先做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">六四燭光 遍地開花<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"c368ca174020ee0d0ff132c91d82df124eaca8a5","tid":2050813,"uid":225100,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T10:55:19.000Z","msg":"可能有人會話呢個係一個反抗獨裁極權嘅手勢 會唔會以為係港獨手勢阿?<br />\n的確有咁嘅可能 但最初呢個手勢唔係咁嘅意思<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">令呢個手勢變成反抗象徵嘅係獨裁政權</span><br />\n只有獨裁政權先會連一個手勢 一個集會都容不下<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">令人民反抗嘅永遠係邪惡獨裁政權</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wcenhpP37sg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwcenhpP37sg&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraY0PclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=fe914148\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wcenhpP37sg</a>"},{"pid":"7049ca2093c02692c366abde4aa4b1fd2eafc17b","tid":2050813,"uid":225100,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T10:58:52.000Z","msg":"五大訴求手勢簡單易明 但始終要兩隻手 唔夠方便<br />\n同埋同六四有少少唔夾"},{"pid":"a76c163a135b62088db08b541746dbe95a0abe8b","tid":2050813,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T11:01:28.000Z","msg":"If we burn"},{"pid":"5a0003efa1fa7898789e722ca52d5fb4d874cf61","tid":2050813,"uid":2251